year $4560,000. Estimates\nplaced the value of this year\u2019s catch\nat less than $300,000.\nSTATE OF OHIO, GITY OF TCLEDO, gg\nLUCAS COUNTY, 3\nFrank J. Chenoy makes oats that he is senior\npartner of the firm of W, J. Cheney Co., doiog\nbusiness in the City of Toledo County aud State\na\u2018oresaid, and that said firm will pay the sun of\nONE HUNDRED DOLLARB for ocach and\novery case of Catarrh that cannot be cured by\nthe use [of Hall's Catarrh Cure.\nFRANK J. CHENEY.\nBworn to before m* and subscribed in pres\nence, this 6th day ot Decem\u201cer, A. D, 1586,\nA. W. GT.RABON\n{Boal.) NOTARY PUBLIC\nAall\u2019s Catarrh Cure is taken internally, and\nucts diroctly on the blood and mucous surfaces\nof the system. Bend for testimounials free,\nF.J CHENEY CO,, Toledo, O,\nSold by all Druggiste, is\u00a2c\nTake Hall's Family Pills for constipation,\nSore Nipples.\nAny mother who has had experience\nwith this distrossing ailment will\nbe pleased to know that a cure umyi\nbe eftected by applying Chamberlain's\nSalve as soon as the child is done!\nnursing. Wipe it off with a soft\ncloth before allowing the babe to\nnurse. Many trained nurses use this\nsalve with best results. For sale by\nDaniel\u2019s drug store. mwf\nSoRCD T g\nFor 80 days the Grand Union Tea\nCo. will have on exhibition at 117\nSouth Pike's Peak avenue, Floreunce,\nsamples of their goods and premiums.\nOall and see us. 76-81\nSIX ATTORNEYS DISBARRED.\nWashington,June I\u2014Six prominent\nWashington attorneys have been dis\nbarred from practice in the depart\nment of the intericr after today. It\nis alleged that they sought out old\nsoldiers or their widows to whom\nland grants had not been issued and\ninformed them that such land could\n\u2018be had on application. When the\n\u2018warrants were issued the lawyers ad\n:viwd the holders that the land conld\n\u2018be sold at uominal figure, In most\ncases the veteraus would agree, the\niland becoming the property of the\nlawyers, who sold it at a large profit.\nThe lawyers disbarred are \u2018'homas\n\u2018R. Harney and Eugene E. Stevens\n\u2018forming the firm of Milo B. Stevens\nand Oo.; Harvey Spaulding, Edwin\nW. Spaulding and James H. Spauld\ning, forming the firm of H. Spaunlding\nand Sons, and Edgar P. Gaddis\nState Convention Pharmacal asso\nciation, Glenwood Springs, June i7,\n1908, via D. and R. G. Dates of\nl ale June 16, and 17. Final limit to\ne turn 10 days from date of sale.\n9.90 for round trip. C. G. Hitch\ncock, Agt. tf\nStomach Troubles.\nMany remarakble cures of stomach\ntroubles have been effected by Cham\nberlain's Stomach and Liver Tablets\nOne man who had spent over two\nthousand dollars for medicine and\ntreatment was cured by a few boxes\nof these tablets. Price, 25 cents.\nSamples free at Danfel\u2019s drug store.\nmwi\nOPPORTUNITIES IN LAND SOUTH\nOne fare plus $2.00 to certain points\nin Texas and New Mexico and return\nfor homeseekers, via Colorado and\nSounthern; liberal limit and stop\novers, Full information on applica\ntion. T. E. Fisher, General Passgen\nger Agent.\nThe Daily Tribune, 40c a month,\nH. HousTON\nis prepared to do all kinds of\nAll work guaranteed.\nShop 202 Pike\u2019s Peak Ave,\nWall Paper, Paint, Glass, Oil\nVarnish, Brushes and Paint\ners' Supplies. 103 E. Main.\nBardwell Benjaman\nCEMENT BLOCK\nContractors and Builders\nLOT 62, SEC. 4. BEAVER PARK\u2018\n\u2014SEE\u2014\n\nS.W.LEE\n'The Furniture Man for New and\nSecond Hand Furniture,\n122 West Main St.\n\no\n4\nB }p\ng e\n\nThe latest report from high socletg\nindicates that Cupid is getting a roug\ndeal. The latest report from this mod\nern laundry eutnbliu%omentls that every\none is \u00a53tting a square deal and always\nwill. ou will find it worth your while\nto.entrust us with the handling of the\nmost delicate fabrice for theve is no pos\nsibility of our irjuring them in any way,\nfor we use no acids or other injurious\nsubstances in our laundrying. We want\nto be favored with your continued pat\nronag